Home Shopping NEtwork Inc saidits Silver King Broadcasting Co INc unit entered a definitivecontract to buy the broadcasting assets of TV station KWVT,Channel 22 in the Portland/Salem, Ore. area for undisclosedterms.    Additionally, the company said KWVT, which serves 785,000homes, began broadcasting Home Shopping Network full time thismorning under an affiliation agreement.    Home Shopping also said it entered a definitive contract tobuy TV Station KPST, Channel 66 in San Francisco and KLTJ,Channel 49 in Dallas. Reuter&#3;